OL,3,CUS bank fires employees for faking
OL,4,Cwork by pretending activity on
OL,5,Ccomputers
OL,7,FAn American bank has fired more than a
OL,8,Fdozen employees for faking work by
OL,9,Fpretending to be active on their
OL,10,Fcomputers.
OL,12,FWells Fargo fired employees in May
OL,13,Ffrom its wealth and investment
OL,14,Fmanagement unit after a review of
OL,15,F"allegations involving simulation of
OL,16,Fkeyboard activity creating an
OL,17,Fimpression of active work," Bloomberg
OL,18,Freported.
