OL,3,CUS bank fires employees for faking
OL,4,Cwork by pretending activity on
OL,5,Ccomputers
OL,7,FWhile the specific devices or software
OL,8,Fused are unclear, employees are
OL,9,Falleged to have used tools like mouse
OL,10,Fmovers or jigglers to imitate work
OL,11,Factivity.
OL,13,FThese tools, designed to simulate
OL,14,Frandom mouse movements, gained
OL,15,Fpopularity during the Covid-19
OL,16,Flockdowns. They are currently sold on
OL,17,FAmazon for as little as #6.
