OL,7,FA Wells Fargo spokesperson said:
OL,8,F"Wells Fargo holds employees to the
OL,9,Fhighest standards and does not
OL,10,Ftolerate unethical behaviour."
OL,12,FTo combat the use of mouse movers,
OL,13,Fsome employers have adopted employee
OL,14,Fmonitoring software, also known as
OL,15,F'bossware', to oversee workers'
OL,16,Fcomputers from a central location.
