OL,7,FAshley Herd, founder of management
OL,8,Ftraining firm Manager Method, said:
OL,9,F"The sad part is that employees feel
OL,10,Fthe need to purchase and use a mouse
OL,11,Fjiggler, and that's a symptom of a
OL,12,Fmuch larger problem."
OL,14,FIn 2016, the San Francisco-based firm
OL,15,Fspent billions settling civil and
OL,16,Fcriminal charges over a scheme which
OL,17,Fled to more than two million fake
OL,18,Faccounts being opened without
OL,19,Fcustomers' consent or knowledge.
